text: Phryneta asmarensis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1969. It is known from Eritrea.BioLib.cz - Phryneta asmarensis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1969
